What do you think about me?
16:54 - to get closer to each other
when it is just the two of you,
ask him how he feels about you.
The Suspension Bridge Effect (the last resort?!)
Change the swaying of the bridge into the swaying of his heart!
The Suspension Bridge Effect (the last resort?!)
Change the swaying of the bridge into the swaying of his heart!
The school festival is our chance to gain some recognition!
All we do is waste our time here in this club room!
Where is all this motivation coming from?
I ask you, what have we accomplished in this club?
so now she wants to reform this club so everybody will be all,
Nibutani-san, you are a miracle worker!
You actually managed to reform that club?
So I ask you, can you live with that?
What ever happened to you joining the Light Music Club?
We can still show the world that we exist!
If we act now, we can succeed!
Nothing's going to come between her and me.
And that is why I want us to do something for the school festival.
Who died and made you boss?!
Master is the head of this organization!
I refuse to conform to the activities of other organizations.
Furthermore, the general public must not learn of our existence.
You were actively recruiting members when you started the club.
Oriental Magick Napping Society in Summer
Did not that involve informing the general public?
Still, all the other clubs have already reserved all the classrooms and activities.
There is not even space to set up another stall.
And that right there is why neither of you has a girlfriend yet.
Do you already have something in mind?
Our club will go down in history as a legend!
And so, we approached the halfway point of the second term,
and I still had not had a proper talk with Rikka
since that night during summer vacation.
I saw one of those on TV!
They pretend to be regular people on the street,
then suddenly start singing and dancing, right?
We will go around the school doing something like that during the festival.
Mind telling me what this is?
I was thinking about what we should do,
and I decided that a battle would get us the most attention.
But you do it all the time.
Why do not you do it, Miss Mori Summer?
I will curse you to death.
I am done with that kind of stuff.
I am done with it too!
do not you want to see the Dark Flame Master restored to his true form?
You guys have not been going home together lately, right?
I do not know why, but she is been like this ever since we went to the beach.
I did not do anything to her!
Sure, she slept over at my place, but...
I really did not do anything!
You were all alone with her at night!
And you had the nerve to do something without me, her servant?
Well, you know that... Unseen Horizon thing?
She insisted on going out to look for it.
What are you all synchronized for?!
I kept quiet about everything else.
I did not say a thing about her dad, going back to her old house,
getting into a fight with Touka-san...
She is probably still worrying about it.
Okay, I am off to work.
I cannot sit down to eat.
I have to leave for work.
He is watching me from the other side of the Horizon.
She must believe that with all her heart.
Care to explain how you got under there?
I was on the gymnastics team in high school.
So these are the types of girls you are into?
I would better be careful around you.
What is the deal this time?
She never liked talking to me in the first place,
but she has not been finishing her lunch lately.
She barely even touches her dinner.
Is it because of what happened back home?
What the heck was that for?!
I am a little disappointed at how useless you are.
You are always hanging around Rikka.
Do not take it out on me.
If you are that worried, why not ask her yourself?
I am supposed to look like a big sister to her.
Doing a good job at keeping them off the rest of your food, I see.
You are actually going to eat them?
Why is she just lying there?
Is she putting on some kind of performance?
Are you being affected by the space division too?
I was just napping here since it is so nice out today.
You are being influenced by space division, brought about by a dark singularity.
We need to do something about this.
It is because of that dark singularity.
I regret taking him into the Administration Bureau's territory.
I should have known they would cast some manner of spell on him.
I have not noticed anything different about him.
Normal people are unable to sense it.
But the Tyrant's Eye is reacting to it.
I am doing everything within my power to contain it.
If I lose my concentration for even a moment, blood may gush forth from every pore on my body.
When I am near Yuuta, my heart rate increases, and I have to get away.
Is that why you have not told him?
And Yuuta's eyes are dangerous right now.
Something comes into me whenever I look into them
and runs rampant throughout my body!
It is all the work of that singularity.
How are you going to get rid of it?
I hoped that he would destroy the singularity of his own will as the Dark Flame Master,
We will have to use force.
It will be dangerous, but we have no choice.
I will fight alongside you through any Ragnarok!
You are truly a faithful servant.
Such is the duty of a contractor.
Can you help me with this question?
Then these two will have the same areas.
Regardless, I never imagined the Dark Flame Master would fall victim to such a spell!
When the moon is next full.
I split it like you said, but I cannot solve it.
Guess I will have to show you again.
Togashi-kun and Takanashi-san cannot make it?
The moon is full tonight, after all.
It is part of the room's feng shui.
